<p>Wearing a plain black top with matching patent bottoms, Katie boosted her golden locks with extra-long extensions, which fell beyond her shoulders.</p>

<p>Highlighting her famous looks with a rich palette of makeup, the TV personality accessorised with a pair of gold pendant necklaces.</p>

<p>With a face mask resting around her wrist, the star sat with her two feet elevated in casts as she prepared to make her way home from the hospital.</p>

