<p>For his part, hunky Carl looked casually cool in a white T-shirt, which he teamed with a pair of distressed jeans and running shoes.</p>

<p>Her outing comes after she took to Instagram to share a snap from her wheelchair as she reflected on her 'tough journey' and reassured fans she's 'feeling stronger and determined' on Saturday.</p>

<p>One week earlier, Katie announced that she was taking a break from social media to heal after breaking both her feet and ankles in a horror accident.</p>

<p>Katie shared a recent snap of her sat in her wheelchair with her booted feet, and wrote: 'Happy Saturday. I’m back online and just want to thank everyone for all the love and support! </p>

